angelic.Name: angelic
angelic.Description: of or belonging to angels; sharing characteristics with that of an angel.

demonic.Name: demonic
demonic.Description: of or belonging to demons; sharing characteristics with that of a demon.

divine.Name: divine
divine.Description: of or relating to a god, especially the Supreme Being.

extraplanar.Name: extraplanar
extraplanar.Description: of or beyond the planes of existence.

extraterrestrial.Name: extraterrestrial
extraterrestrial.Description: of or from outside the earth or its atmosphere.

heavenly.Name: heavenly
heavenly.Description: of, belonging to, or coming from the heaven of God, the angels, etc.

hellish.Name: hellish
hellish.Description: of or belonging to devils; sharing characteristics with that of a devil.

interplanar.Name: interplanar
interplanar.Description: of or belonging to a different plane of existence.

intraplanar.Name: intraplanar
intraplanar.Description: from within a plane of existence.

satanic.Name: satanic
satanic.Description: characteristic of or befitting Satan; extremely wicked; devillike; diabolical.

terrestrial.Name: terrestrial
terrestrial.Description: pertaining to, consisting of, or representing the earth as distinct from other planets.
